author: Mukund Deshpande and George Karypis
title: Using conjunction of attribute values for classification
window: We performed our experiments using a 10 way cross validation scheme and computed average accuracy across different runs. We ran our experiments using a support threshold of 1.0% for all the datasets, except hepati, horse where we used a support threshold of 2.0% and for lymph and zoo we used the support threshold of 5.0%.
